              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/42280833/" class="">第443页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/122920364/" class=" " title="千重子">千重子</a>
              
                <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="42280833">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">真是鬼使神差，这只能说是那总在把我往绝路上拖拽的盲目宿命在作祟，否则无法解释我为何如此的荒唐无稽。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2017-03-12 16:18</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <p>真是鬼使神差，这只能说是那总在把我往绝路上拖拽的盲目宿命在作祟，否则无法解释我为何如此的荒唐无稽。</p>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







